description: Lists all the applications registered with AWS Systems Manager for SAP.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: The filter of name, value, and operator. (dict) --- A specific result obtained by specifying the name, value, and operator. The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values The operator for the filter.

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values.

nested_items.name: Applications
nested_items.description: The applications registered with AWS Systems Manager for SAP.

nested_items.name: DiscoveryStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the latest discovery.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the application.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.
